   version stable 1.1-20080819
   require ncurses
      opts --bindir=/bin
  category utility
 attribute console solo
    source ftp://invisible-island.net/dialog/dialog-$VERSION.tgz
      info home  http://invisible-island.net/dialog/
      info docs  http://invisible-island.net/dialog/manpage/dialog.html
  estimate 200
      desc 'program for allowing shell scripts to do menu driven interaction with users
dialog lets you to present a variety of questions or display messages
using dialog boxes from a shell script (or any scripting language).
These types of dialog boxes are implemented: yes/no box, menu box,
input box, message box, text box, info box, guage box, checklist box,
file selection box, and radiolist box.'
